# Language: English only

All project text must be in **English**:

- Documentation (`docs/`, `README.md`, Cursor rules)
- Code comments (Go, TypeScript, SCSS, etc.)
- User-facing strings in the plugin UI (unless i18n is explicitly added later)
- Commit messages and PR descriptions (team convention)

Do not add or leave Russian (or other non-English) prose in docs or comments. When editing existing files, translate any non-English text you touch or that is clearly outdated.

Exception: third-party quoted content (e.g. upstream API error names) may stay as-is.
